org.janelia.flyem.neuprinter.model

Class ConnectionSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.janelia.flyem.neuprinter.model.ConnectionSet

  • public class ConnectionSet
extends java.lang.Object
    A class representing a ConnectionSet node, which contains the Synapse nodes connecting a presynaptic body to a postsynaptic body. Each ConnectionSet has a presynaptic bodyId, a postsynaptic bodyId, and a set of synapse locations (represented by string keys in the format "x:y:z").
